text: A wid iumnen! Ur keccmet ar texxamin n Nnbi, ar awen iaammed, d inebgawen ar wucci, ur teggunim. Maca, ma tepwaaovem, kecmet. Mi teccam, sahlet; ur ssioxiset ameslay. Ayagi, s tidep, iqelleq Nnbi. Isetea segwen. Oebbi ur Ipsetei $ef tidep. Ma tessutrem asent ta$awsa, ssutret ep deffir tsabert. Yif it wakka, i tezdeg n wulawen nnwen, akked wulawen nnsent. Ur awen ilaq ara a pjjerim Amazan n Oebbi, ne$ a ppa$em tilawin is, deffir es, d awez$i. Ayagi, ad yili, ar Oebbi, d lefviea
